social_posts.post_text: Posting my recap a little late but wanted to express how grateful I am for all your support this past year. ❤️🙏 Looking forward to an amazing 2023! 🫶🥳
Yaa Buoyyy, It’s a-boat time! 🛟🚢 Follow @edc_sea for the full reveal tomorrow ⚡️🌼 ⚓️
Happy Valentine’s Day to my rave fam 🫶
Great to be out here in Mexico! 🇲🇽 Everything looked beautiful at the site walk through last night. 😍 Excited to feel all of your energy today as we kick off Day 1 of @edc_mexico 🙌🥳 ¡VAMOS!

MUCHAS GRACIAS from the entire @edc_mexico team and I to all of the beautiful people who supported us and brought all of the positive energy this past weekend. 🫶 It was an honor to meet so many of you. Grateful for all your love & can’t wait to see you next year 🙏 TE AMO MÉXICO ❤️🇲🇽
Smile! 😃 @beyondwland weekend is almost here!🐰🌀❤️ I hope you’re as excited as I am. Blessed to have this life, can’t wait to be with all of you 🫶

I’ll never forget my first rave. It was 1991, and a ripple of collective joy filled the space. People of all walks of life had traveled to be there, and in that moment I knew that my journey in this new world was only just beginning. Not long after that, Insomniac was born. 🙏 
We’ve come a long way together in these last 30 years, and I am so deeply privileged to be celebrating this milestone with all of you.
I still feel like we’re only just beginning. I can’t wait for the next thirty years. 🥳
Hip hip hoorave!! 😀 I love all you beautiful people! Night one was a blast! Night two let’s go!  @beyondwland 🍄🔈🎶

I can’t stop smiling from this weekend’s @beyondwland trip down the rabbit hole! 🐰🌀

Nearly 170,000 headliners unified to create the most beautiful energy & excitement that could be felt in all areas of the festival. I love meeting so many of you! ❤️ We also kicked off Insomniacs 30 year celebration & it was heartwarming to see how many of you were enjoying Anniversary Lane and taking pictures with EyeCon! 👁️‍🗨️

Special weekends like these remind me how much this community can help energize and inspire us through our daily lives.! 🫶

Thank you for showing up, for bringing the energy, and for being part of the Insomniac family. I hope you all had as much fun as I did and I look forward to seeing you all again for next years Beyond! 🥳
😂😂😂 Just had to fine tune everything. The wait is over… I’ll be dropping the @edc_lasvegas lineup here tomorrow! Thank you for being so patient 🙏❤️🎶🔊

Your #EDCLV2023 lineup has arrived! 
It’s an honor to have so many amazing acts with us this year⚡️🌈

This edition of @EDC_LasVegas we focus on #kineticAWAKENING! 👁✨

Over the past two years, we searched for peace with kineticZEN, then focused on our growth with kineticBLOOM. In 2023, our journey culminates in our collective AWAKENING! 

The kineticAWAKENING is what brings the whole world into alignment, and opens our eyes to this moment together. We celebrate our rebirth in this turning point within our community. Bring the energy to the dancefloor—the new dawn awaits! 

I can’t wait for you all to see the new #kineticFIELD stage design along with many more surprises in store at #EDCLV2023. 

I’ll see you Under the Electric Sky….

Hey, Headliners!

I hope you're feeling the anticipation for our upcoming EDC adventure! As we near our journey, I wanted to provide you with an important travel update to ensure your trip to Las Vegas goes smoothly.

If you’re flying to Vegas, it’s important to know there is ongoing construction at Harry Reid International Airport/McCarran Airport that has resulted in regular flight delays. If you’re driving, know there is construction along the 15 freeway on the way to Vegas that is causing delays depending on the time of day.

If you have the flexibility to adjust your travel plans, you may want to consider arriving earlier as these potential issues are likely to be exacerbated with so many ravers coming  to town. I highly recommend keeping in touch with your airlines to stay up to date on any flight schedule changes or other important information. 

We’re dedicated to making this weekend one of the most incredible experiences of your life. If you run into any obstacles that are outside all of our control, I kindly ask that you approach them with a positive mindset, making a conscious effort not to let them ruin your weekend. Unexpected curveballs can happen before, during, and after a major festival like EDC. Remember to be your best self, immerse yourself in music, engage in games, socialize, and connect with fellow Headliners who may be waiting alongside you. Let's create an atmosphere of positivity and keep the good vibes flowing with your help.

Your excitement and presence means the world to us, and we're genuinely committed to ensuring this adventure surpasses all expectations. 
Let's embark on an unforgettable journey at EDC together!

Wishing you safe travels, and see you all soon!

-Pasquale

Greetings EDC Headliners!

The long-awaited EDC weekend is finally upon us, and we couldn't be more excited to have you here with us. Your presence brings incredible energy and makes this experience truly special. 🌼✨

As you make your way to your HOME for the weekend, I encourage you to embrace the spirit of community and connection. Take a moment to introduce yourself to who you’re dancing next to, extend a helping hand to a fellow raver in need, and spread those GOOD VIBES all around. 😎🫶

We understand that even the best-laid plans may require some adjustments along the way. If there's anything you need assistance with or if you encounter any challenges, please don't hesitate to reach out. Our team is here to support you and ensure that you have the best possible weekend. 👁️‍🗨️💜

Remember, this adventure is about creating unforgettable memories, immersing yourself in the music, and embracing the joyous atmosphere that EDC offers. Let's make this experience a collective CELEBRATION of LOVE, UNITY, and PURE BLISS. ❤️✨

From the bottom of my heart, THANK YOU for being a part of this journey. You being present and bringing your positive energy is what makes EDC. 🙏⚡️

Wishing you an incredible weekend filled with magical moments and lifelong connections. 🌎🤝

Let the festivities begin! 🔊🎶

UPGRADED STICKER & PIN PICKUP INFO! 🔔

As you all know, we have new stickers and pins for all of you at @EDC_LasVegas and they’re here! There is a dedicated sticker and pin pick up area just inside of gate B, as well ANY info booth inside the festival. You can come grab them anytime throughout the weekend. See you all soon! 😍🫶

THANK YOU for an unforgettable weekend HOME at @edc_lasvegas. The ENERGY and LOVE we experienced from all of YOU was truly indescribable.

EDCLV23 was more than just a celebration of music, art, and community; it was a testament to the spirit that has bound ravers around the world.

Reflecting on the past 30 years of Insomniac fills me with indescribable gratitude & emotion. What started as a simple dream has blossomed into a global family united by a love for music, community, and the ultimate rave experience. Each step of this incredible journey has been made possible by your unwavering support.

To the artists who graced our stages & moved us to our core, I offer my deepest gratitude. Your music becomes the soundtrack to our lives, woven into our cherished memories. Your artistry touches hearts, ignites our spirits & reminds us of the universal language that unites us all.

To the Insomniac team, your tireless commitment & unwavering dedication leave me in awe. Year after year, you bring our dreams to life, transforming landscapes into awe-inspiring wonderlands. You are our backbone that drives us forward. 

And finally, to you, the Headliners— Thank YOU. You are the heartbeat that sustains us, the source of inspiration that fuels our passion. Your smiles, hugs, creativity & infectious energy remind us why we embarked on this journey. The magic that envelops us at every festival is a reflection of the love within each & every one of you.

As we close out #EDCLV2023 and continue to celebrate 30 years of Insomniac, let’s carry this energy & love forward. Let us uplift, inspire, and celebrate the beauty of the human spirit. The power of music and community knows no bounds & together, we can create a world filled with more compassion, understanding & boundless joy.

Thank you, from the depths of my heart, for being part of this extraordinary journey. Here's to you, to 30 years of Insomniac, and the countless chapters yet to be written.

Mark your calendars for #EDCLV2024 on May 17, 18 & 19. We have incredible experiences and surprises in store, and I can't wait to share them with all of you. Let's continue spreading Peace, Love, & EDC ✌️❤️

Woke up in camp this morning and found myself in a ghost town 😂 Already experiencing the #EDCBlues 💙

But don't worry, because we're already gearing up for an even more epic #EDCLV2024! ✨

We're taking all your feedback to heart and already working on noting necessary changes while everything is still fresh in our minds. ❤️🧠

Exciting plans are already in motion and we're grateful for your input. 🙏📝

To start off, we'll be bringing back an extra access point into the the KineticFIELD and adding even more effects like flames and fireworks atop our new 100 ft towering structures that surround the stage. And of course, we're designing a brand new stage to bring another unique experience! 😍🔥

We'll also be fine-tuning the festival site layout for smoother flow throughout the grounds. And that's just the beginning—we have a whole list of upgrades and tweaks lined up to ensure an even better experience! 🫶 

Oh, and by the way, we'll fix the signage on a few concession stands so you know we're not actually selling pizza slices for 10k each! 🍕💰

Mark your calendars for MAY 17+18+19, because we're counting down the days till we reunite! Here's a pro tip: Set your alarms for 10AM PT TOMORROW to snag our first batch of Future Owl tickets!

Get ready for another mind-blowing adventure at EDC! Let's dance, laugh, and create unforgettable memories together. See you soon! ✨🎉
The #EDCBlues have hit me like never before 💙🥹

Been living in the Rave since 93! Here with my long time friend @grahamfunke at last years @nocturnalwland! 🌙 It holds a special place in my heart, being the very first “massive” I organized after countless Insomniac warehouse parties. This annual gathering is a cherished time where familiar faces from those early days reunite, and the memories flood back like a beautiful reunion. It's a testament to the timeless bonds we've forged, fueled by the love for music and connection. 🫶 

This is one of my favorite raves of the year and I can’t wait to unite with you all again! If you missed it, I've included the lineup—simply swipe ➡️ Let's embrace the darkness together, dance our hearts out, and create more unforgettable moments. 🕺💜✨ #NocturnalWonderland #30YearsOfInsomniac #GratefulForTheJourney

Between Beyond PNW and last weekend, I found myself lost in my thoughts. While @electric_forest and @daytripla were approaching, my heart remained heavy.

During the weekend, I received an overwhelming amount of warmth from family, friends, artists, Headliners and many amazing people I had the chance to meet. Your hugs and heartfelt messages meant a lot to me. As I reflected on the events that unfolded, I brought my kids Rainbow and Forest with me to EF, and I was grateful to spend quality time with them before flying to Day Trip on Sunday. This weekend really helped put me in a healthy mindset, and I felt a profound connection to the community everywhere I went.

Following the tragic events, I made the decision last week to halt all posting from Insomniac channels out of respect for everyone involved, with the exception of essential information related to the weekend's events. This week, we have started slowly rolling out posts again. For those that attended @beyondwlandpnw, refund information will be available soon as we are just finalizing the logistics of giving the option to receive a full refund or donate to the victim’s families. While we will resume posting, we have not taken this situation lightly. It's not about moving on, but rather about reinforcing the importance of unity and togetherness. These values keep the spirit of our community alive for those who need it. Thank you all for coming together, regardless of where you joined us, and for making this weekend so special during a difficult time. ❤️

Inside was the soundtrack for @edc_sea’s maiden voyage!🎶🚢 

Now even more excited to join together on November 4th to sail into the horizon & chase the sun 🌊🌤️ #EDSea #AdventureAwaits

Thanks to everyone who joined and supported us in producing a new @hardfest experience this past weekend 🙏. We combined the LA Coliseum, BMO stadium and Expo Park in the heart of Los Angeles for the very first time. 

The return of HARD to its LA roots was a special moment. Revisiting the iconic Coliseum brought back nostalgic memories of the old EDC days. 

Thanks to all of the artists who came and played amazing sets, special b2b’s, & other incredible performances that made it a memorable weekend.🧠🗃️

There’s no doubt that challenges arose during the show. Sometimes, doing something that’s never been done before can be difficult. We've heard your feedback loud and clear. Your comments about water stations, VIP, and crowd flow are genuinely appreciated and your input always helps us improve. 💜 We're already working on improvements for next year. If we’re not able to make the necessary changes, we will find a new home in the future. Thank you for trusting us, showing patience, and representing what LA is all about. 🙏
2 parties. 2 cities. New Year’s Weekend. More artists TBA! Swipe for details ➡️ @forevermidnightfest

It all started with this. 28 years ago we followed our dreams and created @nocturnalwland. It all began after organizing Insomniac warehouse parties from 93-94 in the greater Los Angeles area. Nocturnal was our first Insomniac massive, and we never imagined it would become America's longest-running rave. Every year since '95, you've shaped Nocturnal Wonderland into a uniquely magical experience. Seeing OGs from the first Nocturnal dancing with first-timers filled my heart with joy. To all of you, headliners, artists, and crew who made this year's Nocturnal special, my deepest gratitude. From my heart, thank you for an incredible weekend—can't wait for next year 🙏❤️👁️‍🗨️

I wanted to share some #CampEDC updates for #EDCLV2024. We've been listening to your feedback and making improvements in order to make this year better than ever. 

🚌 TRANSPORTATION: 
For those getting shiftpods, expect continuous tram service to get you and your #CampEDCFam at several points within the parking lots to Camping check-in and then again after check-in there will be several convenient tram stops throughout camping.

😎 SHADE ADDITIONS: We're adding shade structures & misting lines located outside showers to keep you cool while you wait to refresh. 

🔌 RV POWER: More power will be provided to help prevent outages. We've upgraded the power infrastructure to be able to segregate RV's and Shiftpods. This will ensure RV's do not impact ShiftPod power service. 

☎️ SERVICE TEAMS: Additional dedicated teams will be deployed for RV and Shiftpods to speed up response time should any issues arise. 

We're working hard for an unforgettable #CampEDC 2024 on The Mesa! 💫

PRESALE INFO: 
🌈 Loyalty Presale for last year's Campers with #EDCLV2024 passes starts THIS THURSDAY at 10am PT.

🌈 General Presale for all #EDCLV2024 Future Owl presale  begins THIS FRIDAY at 10am PT.

Stay tuned for email updates, and check campedc.com for all the details 💌⛺️
Nocturnal creatures in their natural habitat 🦉🦝🐸

*drum roll* 🥁 Your themes for our @EDC_Sea Maiden Voyage are here! 

Swipe 👉 to check out the theme for each of our days & nights on the Electric Sea. I can’t wait to see all of the creative outfits you Headliners come up with!

I’m counting down the days til we embark on this brand new experience together. Drop your must bring items in the comments so I don’t forget anything! 🫡⚓️❤️🌊

Fresh off EDSea & in a state of complete BLISS! A bit bruised, sleep-deprived, & slightly wrecked, but already want to go back! 💪🥰

The ENERGY, MUSIC, ART, & most importantly, the beautiful SOULS that filled EDSea created a truly one-of-a-kind experience. Your PASSION & POSITIVITY illuminated every corner of the ship, turning it into a floating paradise of LOVE & UNITY. 🛳️❤️

Having the chance to hang out & share intimate moments with both artists & Headliners made every second uniquely SPECIAL. My heartfelt thanks to those who took a moment to say hello and even grabbed a photo with me. 🙏

I want to express my gratitude to the amazing artists, performers, entire @insomniacevents family, @sxmliveloud, @vibeepresents, & @norwegiancruiseline, who worked tirelessly to bring this epic experience to life. Your dedication & hard work in making EDSea a reality are truly beyond words. ✨

To show our appreciation for everyone who supported our first-ever EDSea, all of you who joined us this year will have the first opportunity to secure a pass for next year. And if you couldn't make it this time, you can still sign up to be in line. This doesn't obligate you to purchase, but it ensures you have a place to book if you decide to do so. Keep an eye on your emails for the invite. 💌👀

I love each and every one of you, & I can't thank you enough for making this incredible journey unforgettable. Thank you, thank you, from the bottom of my heart , and I can't wait to see you all next year on the Electric Sea #EDSEA24  🏖️

Your incredible energy, passion, and love made this year's @edc_orlando one for the books! 📚✨ Your smiles and positive vibes are the heartbeat of EDC. ❤️ Thanks to each and every one of you who supported and made it all possible. 🙏😎 #PLUR247 #365AllDayAllNight

From the Electric Sea in the Caribbean to the Electric Sky in Orlando – 8 days, 2 festivals, countless memories. A huge thank you to all the Headliners who came out and to all the dedicated Insomniacs who made it all happen! Hoping everyone had a blast during the EDC marathon!

This chillaxing moment, captured during our Pajama Jam party on the ship amidst the festival frenzy, perfectly reflects my current mood. Massive props to the hardcore headliners who rocked both @edc_sea and @edc_orlando – you're the real MVPs of the dance floor! 🙌🎉 

Cheers to the memories and beats that linger long after the music stops.✨ #FestivalProducerLife #insomniacCrew #chillmodeactivated #FestivalAdventures #PajamaJam #DoubleDoseOfEDC #Sprouted

Grateful for the incredible support at our first-ever @apocalypsefest! 🧟 Your infectious energy kept the vibe alive all weekend!

A huge thank you to everyone involved – Headliners, artists, performers, and the hardworking Insomniac teams. You were the true "brrraaaiiinnnss" 🧠 behind the operation, navigating obstacles like seasoned survivors 💪

The team and I had a blast putting this together, and I'm deeply thankful to everyone who joined us this weekend. None of this would have been possible without you 🫶

This weekend confirmed that bass has the power to save the world 🔊❤️
That friend that wakes you up for the afters when you’re trying to go to bed. It’s me, I’m that friend 😂

THANK YOU and HAPPY NEW YEAR to everyone who supported our very first Forever Midnight. ♾️🕛 Walking through the venue, soaking in the music and vibes felt like a rave straight out of the early ‘90s. 😎 All of you who brought your love for music and the energy made the night unforgettable! 🙏 I’m excited to announce we’ll return next year, evolving and ready for more! 🔊🎶
